# cf-kv smoke namespace IDs — single source of truth.
#
# Sourced by provision.sh, teardown.sh, and run-tests.sh. Override
# either via env var (preserves the same defaults if env unset).
#
# When the project's smoke namespace is rotated, change these two
# defaults — three scripts pick up the new IDs automatically.
#
# Both IDs are validated against `^[0-9a-f]{32}$` at the consuming
# site (defensive against tainted env-var injection).

: "${SECRETENV_TEST_CFKV_NAMESPACE_ID:=c554de8d89644f3d85f21933e7aea910}"
: "${SECRETENV_TEST_CFKV_REGISTRY_NAMESPACE_ID:=d3cd960f990946809bc3b50cd4ef119d}"

CFKV_NS="$SECRETENV_TEST_CFKV_NAMESPACE_ID"
CFKV_REG_NS="$SECRETENV_TEST_CFKV_REGISTRY_NAMESPACE_ID"
